WISArD


This code is a Geant4 simulation for the WISArD experiment at CERN. 

v1.0 : 
basic WISArD code with the new geometry.

v2.0 : 
Added a Messenger to interact more easier with some systematic variable.
Developping different trees for each particle.
Move the analysis from DeltaKineticEnergy to TotalEnergyDeposit.


